data.description: Fantastic Location in The Heart of Evans! This 2 Story All Brick 4 BD/2.5 BA Traditional Home with Sitting Porch Nestled in The Waterford Subdivision. Home features Crown Molding & Judges Paneling in Foyer, Family Room with Fire Place and Rear Deck Access. As well as a Formal Dining Room & Flowing Hardwood Flooring. Spacious Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances including Gas Stove, & Refrigerator, Tiled Backsplash, Granite Countertops, and Breakfast Area. Separate Laundry Room and A Half Bath rounds out the Main Level. Upstairs Oversize Owner's Suite showcases Tray Ceiling, Walk-in Closet with Natural Light, Large Owner's Bathroom with Dual Vanities, Large Jetted Soaking Tub and Separate Shower! Three Additional Bedrooms share a Hall Bathroom. Outdoor Entertaining is easy with a Spacious Rear Deck overlooking the Private Backyard. A Two Car Garage welcomes you home. Great home and & location!
